          <msContents>
            <summary>Small manuscript for private or public use and recitation containing two texts. The main text (f. 1r-4r) is focused on mantras for breath exercises. The second text, the Gurupādukāstuti (f. 4r-5v), is a work in praise of a teacher's (guru's) sandals (pādukā); mention of Śakti (feminine power) suggests elements of Tantrism.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
            <msItem>
              <title>Ajapāgāyatrīmantra</title>
              <title type="vernacular">अजपागायत्रीमन्त्र</title>
